column4: UPDATE 1-Tesla  Elon Musk win dismissal of lawsuit over Model 3 production
column5: SAN FRANCISCO  March 25 A federal judge in San Francisco dismissed for the second time a securities fraud lawsuit brought by Tesla Inc shareholders alleging that the company made misleading comments about the production status of its Model 3.
